OL,3,CHow inadequate hospital translation
OL,4,Cservices played a part in baby's death
OL,6,FExpectant mother Hazha is now
OL,7,Fterrified to have another baby at the
OL,8,Fsame hospital, as ITV News Central's
OL,9,FHannah Ludlow reports.
OL,11,FHealth inequality and inadequate
OL,12,Ftranslation services played a part in
OL,13,Fthe death of an unborn baby at a
OL,14,FBirmingham hospital, an investigation
OL,15,Fhas found.
OL,17,FHazha and Bahroz Ghafoor, who live in
OL,18,FBirmingham and are originally from
OL,19,FIraq, had always dreamed of having a
OL,20,Fbig family.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/17
