OL,3,CHow inadequate hospital translation
OL,4,Cservices played a part in baby's death
OL,6,FThey want to share their story to
OL,7,Fprevent other expectant mothers from
OL,8,Fexperiencing what they did, but they
OL,9,Fdo not want their faces shown for fear
OL,10,Fof backlash online.
OL,12,FAfter five failed pregnancies,
OL,13,Fincluding two ectopic pregnancies and
OL,14,Fthree unsuccessful rounds of IVF,
OL,15,FHazha was delighted to finally
OL,16,Fconceive naturally. She decided the
OL,17,Fbaby would be called Mally.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/17
