OL,3,CHow inadequate hospital translation
OL,4,Cservices played a part in baby's death
OL,6,FHowever, on the evening of the 26
OL,7,FSeptember 2023 - at 37 weeks pregnant
OL,8,F- Hazha was admitted to Birmingham
OL,9,FWomen's Hospital with abdominal pain
OL,10,Fand irregular foetal movements.
OL,12,FAfter Mally's heart rate was found to
OL,13,Fbe normal, Hazha, who does not speak
OL,14,FEnglish, was transferred to an
OL,15,Fantenatal ward.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/17
