OL,3,CHow inadequate hospital translation
OL,4,Cservices played a part in baby's death
OL,6,FThe plan had been for a Caesarian
OL,7,Fsection the following morning but,
OL,8,Fjust a few hours later, Baby Mally's
OL,9,Fheart had stopped. A later review
OL,10,Ffound her heartbeat had, in fact, been
OL,11,Fabnormal.
OL,13,FHazha, voiced by an actor, says she is
OL,14,F"constantly crying" and struggles to
OL,15,Flive in the house where she prepared
OL,16,Ffor the arrival of Baby Mally
OL,18,F"This was substandard care"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/17
