OL,6,F"There was negligent care and
OL,7,Ftreatment provided to Mrs Ghafoor
OL,8,Fafter she was admitted into hospital
OL,9,Fon 26 September 2023.
OL,11,F"On the basis of the independent
OL,12,Fexpert evidence obtained the trust
OL,13,Fadmits that there was a failure to
OL,14,Fidentify an abnormal CTG and that this
OL,15,Fwas substandard care."
OL,17,FA report by the Maternity and Newborn
OL,18,FSafety Investigations team found
OL,19,Fmultiple failings in Hazha's care.
OL,21,FThey included:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/17
