OL,3,CHow inadequate hospital translation
OL,4,Cservices played a part in baby's death
OL,6,FThe report highlighted that "health
OL,7,Finequalities relating to ethnicity may
OL,8,Fhave impacted on the care or outcome
OL,9,Fduring the Mother's and the Baby's
OL,10,Fcare".
OL,12,FIt added: "the non-use of interpreting
OL,13,Fservices and the use of a non-neutral
OL,14,Fparty as interpreter may have meant
OL,15,Fthat the tone and urgency of the
OL,16,FMother's concerns were not adequately
OL,17,Funderstood.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/17
