OL,7,Fwhen the Mother was admitted to
OL,8,Ftriage, the details of the type of
OL,9,Fpain she was experiencing, and the
OL,10,Fintensity may have been explored in
OL,11,Fmore depth if an interpreter had been
OL,12,Fused."
