OL,3,CHow inadequate hospital translation
OL,4,Cservices played a part in baby's death
OL,6,FBahroz remembers Birmingham Women's
OL,7,FHospital's video-on-demand service
OL,8,Fbeing faulty. He said: "Every five
OL,9,Fminutes, it was cutting off. They
OL,10,Fbring another one, I see too many
OL,11,Fthings, even two weeks ago it happened.
OL,13,F"There's supposed to be someone there
OL,14,Fto translate to other patients, but
OL,15,Fthere was nothing. They didn't bring
OL,16,Fanyone."
