OL,6,FThe family's lawyer, Wioleta Dworak,
OL,7,Fsays Hazha was failed at every step of
OL,8,Fthe way.
OL,10,FMs Dworak told ITV News Central: "She
OL,11,Fthought that if he was going to leave,
OL,12,Fshe would die, and Mally would die
OL,13,Falong with her.
OL,15,F"She couldn't communicate with any of
OL,16,Fthe members of staff. Even though they
OL,17,Fwere telling her 'everything's ok',
OL,18,Fshe could feel something was wrong.
