OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News Central, he said:
OL,7,F"In 2019, as part of the NHS long term
OL,8,Fplan, a commitment was made that there
OL,9,Fwould be a continuity of care for
OL,10,Fblack, asian, minority ethnic women
OL,11,Fgoing through pregnancy.
OL,13,F"What we discovered by 2022 was that
OL,14,Fthat commitment hadn't been met and
OL,15,Fthey actually rescinded on it. The
OL,16,Freason being was that they hadn't been
OL,17,Fable to recruit significant numbers of
OL,18,Fmidwives."
