OL,6,FIn response, a Department of Health
OL,7,Fand Social Care spokesperson said:"It
OL,8,Fis unacceptable that there are such
OL,9,Fstark inequalities for women and
OL,10,Fbabies, but through our Plan for
OL,11,FChange, this government is determined
OL,12,Fto change that.
OL,14,F"We will support trusts to make rapid
OL,15,Fimprovements, and we will train
OL,16,Fthousands more midwives to support
OL,17,Fwomen throughout their pregnancy and
OL,18,Fbeyond."
