OL,6,FHazha is pregnant again and, whilst
OL,7,Fshe is happy to be expecting, she
OL,8,Ffears the Trust will make the same
OL,9,Fmistakes again.
OL,11,FIn response, Daljit Athwal, Chief
OL,12,FNursing and Midwifery Officer at
OL,13,FBirmingham Women's and Children's NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust, said: "We further
OL,15,Fextend our deepest sympathies to the
OL,16,Ffamily on the loss of their daughter
OL,17,Fand our teams continue to support them.
OL,19,F"Our training compliance has
OL,20,Fconsistently met national standards
OL,21,Fover the last six years.
